<h3>Eye of Tallon</h3>
<p>Yet another upgrade that deserves special attention, this is an upgrade to Eye of Zomm.&nbsp; It turns you invisible, is invisible
itself, can see invisible and zooms your view slightly.&nbsp; This spell lasts a full mnute (whereas Zomm lasts only 30 
seconds).&nbsp; Although this eye was originally safer than Zomm, the June 2002 changes that made mobs completely ignore 
pets, invisibility isn't really important for scouting mobs.&nbsp;&nbsp; The fact that it turns the caster invisible 
might benefit you in certain situations.</p>
<p> Although there is nothing to prevent you from casting this
spell while you have a pet, your pet will suicide when you become
invisible.&nbsp; If you have the Suspend Minion2 AA, this eye won't kill your pet if you suspend it first.&nbsp; </p>

